These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: baseball, parkour, sailing
1. Sport:parkour is on the right of Sport:sailing##1
2. Sport:baseball is on the far right##1
3. Sport:baseball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | sailing | parkour | baseball |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: papaya, zucchini, strawberry
1. Food:zucchini is in an odd position##4
2. Food:papaya is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | papaya | strawberry | zucchini |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: filmmaking, woodworking, cooking
1. Hobby:woodworking is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the left or right of Hobby:cooking##3
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | woodworking | cooking |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
